# ── Jules (Google AI agent) droppings ──
# Jules dumps screenshots/videos/test-scripts at repo root for self-verification.
# These rules target the root only so legit images inside pages/ stay tracked.

# Screenshots and videos (root only)
/*.png
/*.jpg
/*.jpeg
/*.gif
/*.webm
/*.mp4
/videos/

# Test scripts Jules generates to validate its own changes (root only)
/test_script.py
/test_script.js

# Misc Jules artifact directories (root only)
/snapshots/

# Lovable-built projects live in pages/ but are managed by their own .git + GitHub remote.
# Outer repo tracks only the sibling .md marker (e.g. pages/011-git-object-explorer.md).
pages/011-git-object-explorer/
